(Yoruba)                  (English)
Children's Song           Children's Song
L'abe igi orombo          Under the Orange Tree
L'abe igi orombo          Under the orange tree
N'ibe l'agbe nsere wa     Where we play our games
Inu wa dun, ara wa ya     We are happy, we are excited
L'abe igi orombo          Under the orange tree...  

Orombo, orombo            Orange, orange
